data.description: Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, this meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem boasts 1,100 square feet of comfortable living space, providing the perfect blend of coziness and modern elegance. It sits at the end of a well-kept block, with no passing traffic. This home is completely move-in ready, as there are many updates throughout. Beautiful dark walnut floors are the focal point as you walk through this commodious layout. The backyard offers an outdoor oasis with plenty of room for entertaining. There's a full length driveway along with a two car detached garage. This home won't last long. Schedule your showing today!
